description:
after a mistake on my burrito box order on 10/30/11, i called to share what had happened with a manager (not expected anything more than perhaps a free burrito), who confirmed with the store manager and offered to redo the WHOLE order. i'm not comfortable with that since we did, after all, enjoy the burritos provided, but i'm very impressed with their customer service. 

shitpotle? clever! and you thought of that on the toilet? classy, too! 

to the whiny yelpers over the portions at this location: the portions are already too large for healthy consumption and *none* of you look malnourished, so stop complaining, tubbies! (c;
